data.description: A beautifully updated home located in the heart of Limon, just blocks from the school and from downtown. Located on a 7100 sf lot, this home is deceptively large! This home has been beautifully updated, starting with the kitchen which has granite countertops opening up into a large open area and overlooking the family room. The kitchen also features a very large pantry. Upstairs, there is a very large bedroom that function as an office/bedroom as it is spacious enough to have two separate areas. The basement features a large bedroom with a walk-in closet along with a beautifully finished 3/4 bathroom. The backyard is private and spacious and has a concreted porch area and a fire pit area. There is a separate garden area with a garden/tool shed. Attached to the house is a nearly completely enclosed carport make out of wood. This home is move-in-ready and is a hidden gem in the heart of Limon!!! See it today. It won't last long!!! Call to schedule a showing!
